snippet.title: Slender-Man for Android/iPhone - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay for the mobile version of Slender Man for Android and iPhone

Play Slender-Man for iPhone at:
http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/slender-man/id562558324?mt=8

Play Slenderman for Android (Call of Slender) at:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rory.slender
